    public abstract class InputStreamParser
extends Parser
    Subclass of Parser for byte-based parsers.
    Description

    This class is typically the parent class of all byte-based parsers. It has 1 abstract method to implement...

    • parse(InputStream, ClassMeta, ParserContext)
    @Consumes annotation

    The media types that this parser can handle is specified through the @Consumes annotation.

    However, the media types can also be specified programmatically by overriding the Parser.getMediaTypes() method.
